### mangleCoveragePath() {#a9dc80501043000f0bf75820ebfef69c4}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>static std::string mangleCoveragePath (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a> Filename, bool PreservePaths)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Convert a path to a gcov filename.

If PreservePaths is true, this translates &quot;/&quot; to &quot;#&quot;, &quot;..&quot; to &quot;^&quot;, and drops &quot;.&quot;, to match gcov.

Definition at line <a href="#l00639">639</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/profiledata/gcov-cpp">GCOV.cpp</a>.

<Link id="l00520" /><CodeLine lineNumber="520"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Get the total execution count of loops among blocks on the same line.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00521" /><CodeLine lineNumber="521"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Assuming a reducible flow graph, the count is the sum of back edge counts.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00522" /><CodeLine lineNumber="522"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Identifying loops is complex, so we simply find cycles and perform cycle</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00556" /><CodeLine lineNumber="556"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// than 0% and less than 1%.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00557" /><CodeLine lineNumber="557" lineLink="#ac098400c034e9ba009a49e25d47b487d"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">static</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> uint32&#95;t <a href="#ac098400c034e9ba009a49e25d47b487d">formatPercentage</a>(uint64&#95;t dividend, uint64&#95;t divisor) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00560" /><CodeLine lineNumber="560"><Highlight kind="normal">  dividend &#42;= 100;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00561" /><CodeLine lineNumber="561"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">return</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> dividend &lt; divisor ? 1 : dividend / divisor;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00562" /><CodeLine lineNumber="562"><Highlight kind="normal">&#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00563" /><CodeLine lineNumber="563"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00564" /><CodeLine lineNumber="564"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// This custom division function mimics gcov&#39;s branch ouputs:</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00565" /><CodeLine lineNumber="565"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//   - Round to closest whole number</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00566" /><CodeLine lineNumber="566"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//   - Only output 0% or 100% if it&#39;s exactly that value</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00567" /><CodeLine lineNumber="567" lineLink="#ac5c50c19959609312020d2f5e1a0ca71"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">static</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> uint32&#95;t <a href="#ac5c50c19959609312020d2f5e1a0ca71">branchDiv</a>(uint64&#95;t Numerator, uint64&#95;t Divisor) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00571" /><CodeLine lineNumber="571"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">return</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> 100;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00572" /><CodeLine lineNumber="572"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00573" /><CodeLine lineNumber="573"><Highlight kind="normal">  uint8&#95;t Res = (Numerator &#42; 100 + Divisor / 2) / Divisor;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00574" /><CodeLine lineNumber="574"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Res == 0)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00575" /><CodeLine lineNumber="575"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">return</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> 1;</Highlight></CodeLine>
